{
  "texts": [
    "Our pre-annotation strategy is based on three assumptions: Assumption 1.",
    "Our QA task only tackles information extraction (i.e., answering questions) from one single place (a sentence) in the note at a time.",
    "Assumption 2.",
    "The inquired information can be found in a single sentence in the note.",
    "This assumption stems from our rigorous manual exploration of the notes during the note enrichment step, where we find RegEx patterns."
  ]
}